Name "Nether Star Loop"

Every Tick do

    Input 8192 fe: : 
        From Power

    Output 8192 fe: : 
        To Crafter



Every Redstone Pulse Do
        Input 4 nether_star From NetherStar
        Output Retain 4 nether_star To Crafter

Forget

        Input 64 nether_star From Crafter
        Output 64 nether_star To EACH NetherStar

Forget

        Input 256 redstone_block From EMCLink
        Output Retain 256 redstone_block To Crafter Slots 1,2,3,4

End
